# Inventory: Kit-Contributed Roles

## Brief Summary

Kits (and apparatus supportKits) should be able to contribute role definitions to the Loom, alongside — and potentially overridden by — guild-level roles in `guild.json`. Kit-contributed roles are namespaced `{pluginId}.{roleName}`, carry permissions (dependency-scoped), and optionally carry inline instructions or an instructionsFile. A guild-defined role with the same qualified name fully overrides the kit-contributed one.

---

## Affected Code

